sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant FastAPI
    participant Database
    participant Security
    participant Google
    
    Note over User,Google: Standard Username/Password Authentication
    
    User->>Browser: Enter credentials
    Browser->>FastAPI: POST /auth/login
    FastAPI->>Database: Query user by username
    Database-->>FastAPI: User record
    FastAPI->>Security: Verify password hash (Argon2)
    Security-->>FastAPI: Password validation result
    
    alt Password Valid
        FastAPI->>Security: Create JWT token
        Security-->>FastAPI: JWT token (HS256)
        FastAPI->>Browser: Set HttpOnly cookie
        Note over Browser: Cookie attributes:<br/>- HttpOnly: true<br/>- Secure: production<br/>- SameSite: Lax<br/>- Max-Age: 7 days
        Browser-->>User: Login successful
    else Password Invalid
        FastAPI-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        Browser-->>User: Login failed
    end
    
    Note over User,Google: OAuth 2.0 Authentication Flow
    
    User->>Browser: Click "Login with Google"
    Browser->>FastAPI: GET /auth/google
    FastAPI->>Google: Redirect to OAuth authorization
    Note over Google: OAuth 2.0 Authorization<br/>Code Flow with PKCE
    Google-->>Browser: Authorization page
    User->>Google: Grant permissions
    Google->>FastAPI: GET /auth/google/callback?code=...
    FastAPI->>Google: Exchange code for access token
    Google-->>FastAPI: Access token + user info
    
    FastAPI->>Database: Check if user exists
    alt User Exists
        Database-->>FastAPI: Existing user record
    else New User
        FastAPI->>Database: Create new user account
        Database-->>FastAPI: New user record
    end
    
    FastAPI->>Security: Create JWT token
    Security-->>FastAPI: JWT token
    FastAPI->>Browser: Redirect with HttpOnly cookie
    Browser-->>User: Login successful
    
    Note over User,Google: Token Validation on Protected Requests
    
    User->>Browser: Access protected resource
    Browser->>FastAPI: Request with cookie
    FastAPI->>Security: Validate JWT token
    
    alt Token Valid
        Security-->>FastAPI: Decoded payload
        FastAPI->>Database: Get user by username
        Database-->>FastAPI: User record
        FastAPI-->>Browser: Protected resource
        Browser-->>User: Content displayed
    else Token Invalid/Expired
        FastAPI-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized
        Browser-->>User: Redirect to login
    end